        "app_readme": "<p>Notifier App for TrueNAS</p>",
        "detailed_readme": "<h1>firenotifier</h1>\n<p>firenotifier is a notification server that gets triggered by doing a POST call to a REST api. The POST data\nhas a group id and a number of attributes that are used to create the notification message.\nThe notification message then gets sent via SMS or Email to all recipients of the specified group.</p>\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p>This chart bootstraps an firenotifier deployment on a <a href=\"http://kubernetes.io\">Kubernetes</a> cluster using the <a href=\"https://helm.sh\">Helm</a> package manager.</p>\n<h2>Configuration</h2>\n<p>tbd</p>",
